    <sec id="Sec5">
      <title>Calculating significance of pleiotropy</title>
      <p id="Par10">We compute <italic>P</italic> values for the two components of our pleiotropy score using two different procedures, corresponding to two different null expectations.
<list list-type="order"><list-item><p id="Par11">Theoretical <italic>P</italic> values (Raw pleiotropy score [<italic>P</italic><sub><italic>m</italic></sub> and <italic>P</italic><sub><italic>n</italic></sub>] or LD-corrected pleiotropy score [<inline-formula id="IEq7"><alternatives><tex-math id="M13">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
