    </sec>
    <sec id="Sec8">
      <title>Pleiotropy is driven by polygenicity</title>
      <p id="Par17">We applied the permutation-based empirical <italic>P</italic> value calculation (polygenicity/LD-corrected pleiotropy score: <inline-formula id="IEq23"><alternatives><tex-math id="M45">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
