      <p id="Par18">As an additional test of whether the pleiotropy we observe is driven by polygenicity, we calculated the polygenicity of the same 372 heritable traits from the UK Biobank. We measured polygenicity using a version of the genomic inflation factor corrected using LD score <inline-formula id="IEq29"><alternatives><tex-math id="M57">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
