    <sec id="Sec10">
      <title>Pleiotropy score is correlated with molecular and biological function</title>
      <p id="Par21">To further investigate the properties of pleiotropic variants, we examined the effects of various functional and biochemical annotations on our LD-corrected pleiotropy score (<inline-formula id="IEq44"><alternatives><tex-math id="M87">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
